metadata.name: Become One
metadata.description:
Sink me into the millions of grains of your earthly body

Entangle me in your infinite spectrums 

Swallow me into your pink hymns 

Feed your life into my lungs

Bewitch my heart
 
Break my bones 

Ascend my soul 

Merge into me

Become one 

Poetry and Photography by Jerad Armijo “Away I flew”.

Music/Sound Design by Multi-Platinum producer Aeneas "Hardley Davidson" Middleton.
